@startuml sequence-login
actor User
participant "React SPA" as Web
participant "FastAPI" as API
database PostgreSQL as DB

User -> Web: email, password
Web -> API: POST /auth/login
API -> DB: SELECT user
DB --> API: user row
API --> Web: JWT access_token
Web -> Web: save token
Web -> API: GET /users/me (Bearer)
API --> Web: User + role
Web --> User: redirect dashboard
@enduml
